<br>
As to all the postings about SKs and Paladins outtaunting us: YOU chose to live without spells so stop complaining about it. If they outtaunt you while you tank a endmob, stop taunting, let them die and blame it on him, they will stop quickly. If they outtaunt you in a group, be happy, if the healer sleeps they die, not you <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
/em orders another pint of ale<br>
